---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Industries We Serve | Kaya Blue" description="Web solutions for real estate, staffing agencies, and finance.">
<main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 py-20">
<!-- Hero Section -->
<header class="mb-32">
<div class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 mb-6 rounded-full bg-accent/10 border border-accent/20">
<span class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase text-accent" style="">Sectors of Expertise</span>
</div>
<h1 class="text-[3rem] md:text-[4rem] font-black leading-tight tracking-tighter mb-6 text-on-surface" style="">
                Industries We <span class="text-accent" style="">Transform</span>
</h1>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl font-medium leading-relaxed" style="">
                We engineer bespoke digital architectures for sectors where precision, security, and scalability are non-negotiable. Our solutions aren't just platforms—they're competitive advantages.
            </p>
</header>
<!-- Industry Bento Grid -->
<section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 mb-32">
<!-- Real Estate Section -->
<div class="md:col-span-8 bg-surface-container rounded-xl p-8 md:p-12 border border-outline-variant/50 hover:border-accent/50 transition-all group relative overflow-hidden">
<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-8 text-accent/10 group-hover:text-accent/20 transition-colors">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-9xl" style="">domain</span>
</div>
<div class="relative z-10">
<h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-4 tracking-tight" style="">Real Estate</h2>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant mb-10 max-w-lg" style="">Advanced property management systems and immersive digital experiences that accelerate liquidity and simplify asset oversight.</p>
<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
<div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-accent" data-icon="dashboard_customize" style="">dashboard_customize</span>
<div>
<h3 class="font-bold text-on-surface mb-1" style="">Asset Dashboards</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant" style="">Real-time portfolio tracking with integrated IoT data.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-accent" data-icon="vr_pano" style="">vrpano</span>
<div>
<h3 class="font-bold text-on-surface mb-1" style="">Virtual Showcasing</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant" style="">High-performance 3D tours and spatial visualizations.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-accent" data-icon="account_balance" style="">account_balance</span>
<div>
<h3 class="font-bold text-on-surface mb-1" style="">MLS Integration</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant" style="">Seamless data synchronization across global listing services.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-accent" data-icon="contract" style="">contract</span>
<div>
<h3 class="font-bold text-on-surface mb-1" style="">Smart Contracts</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant" style="">Automated leasing agreements and payment escrows.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Trust Stat Card -->
<div class="md:col-span-4 bg-surface-container-high rounded-xl p-8 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center border border-outline-variant/50">
<div class="text-accent font-black text-6xl mb-4" style="">$450M+</div>
<div class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-on-surface-variant mb-6" style="">Transactions Processed</div>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-medium" style="">Through Glodinas-built enterprise fintech architectures since 2021.</p>
</div>
<!-- Staffing Card -->
<div class="md:col-span-6 bg-surface-container rounded-xl p-8 border border-outline-variant/50 hover:border-accent/50 transition-all relative overflow-hidden">
<div class="flex items-center space-x-4 mb-6">
<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-accent" data-icon="groups" style="">groups</span>
</div>
<h2 class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tight" style="">Staffing Agencies</h2>
</div>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant mb-8" style="">Deploying high-frequency recruitment engines that automate the mundane and elevate human potential.</p>
<ul class="space-y-4">
<li class="flex items-center space-x-3 p-3 rounded-lg bg-background/50 border border-outline/30" style="">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-accent text-sm" data-icon="bolt" style="">bolt</span>
<span class="font-medium text-sm" style="">Automated ATS Workflows</span>
</li>
<li class="flex items-center space-x-3 p-3 rounded-lg bg-background/50 border border-outline/30" style="">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-accent text-sm" data-icon="psychology" style="">psychology</span>
<span class="font-medium text-sm" style="">AI-Powered Candidate Matching</span>
</li>
<li class="flex items-center space-x-3 p-3 rounded-lg bg-background/50 border border-outline/30" style="">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-accent text-sm" data-icon="calendar_month" style="">calendar_month</span>
<span class="font-medium text-sm" style="">Dynamic Shift Management</span>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<!-- Finance Card -->
<div class="md:col-span-6 bg-surface-container rounded-xl p-8 border border-outline-variant/50 hover:border-accent/50 transition-all relative overflow-hidden">
<div class="flex items-center space-x-4 mb-6">
<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-accent" data-icon="account_balance_wallet" style="">account_balance_wallet</span>
</div>
<h2 class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tight" style="">Finance &amp; Business</h2>
</div>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant mb-8" style="">Secure, bank-grade digital infrastructure designed for rigorous regulatory environments and high-volume operations.</p>
<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
<div class="p-4 bg-surface-container-low rounded-lg border border-outline-variant/20">
<div class="font-mono text-[10px] text-accent mb-2 uppercase" style="">Compliance</div>
<div class="text-sm font-bold" style="">Regulatory Guardrails</div>
</div>
<div class="p-4 bg-surface-container-low rounded-lg border border-outline-variant/20">
<div class="font-mono text-[10px] text-accent mb-2 uppercase" style="">Security</div>
<div class="text-sm font-bold" style="">End-to-End Encryption</div>
</div>
<div class="p-4 bg-surface-container-low rounded-lg border border-outline-variant/20">
<div class="font-mono text-[10px] text-accent mb-2 uppercase" style="">Analytics</div>
<div class="text-sm font-bold" style="">Predictive Modeling</div>
</div>
<div class="p-4 bg-surface-container-low rounded-lg border border-outline-variant/20">
<div class="font-mono text-[10px] text-accent mb-2 uppercase" style="">Systems</div>
<div class="text-sm font-bold" style="">Legacy ERP Bridges</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Image Break / Visual Buffer -->
<section class="mb-32">
<div class="relative w-full h-80 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
<img alt="Abstract digital network" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale opacity-40 group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700" data-alt="Abstract glowing cyan digital network lines" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDfHQPgMGplreo8oZ6pfxHF3d-JWKY4GhK6g4RFaXSaM2_t4yugx4nC_Um3ILkQDQb-0gfCT_Fla-87AXKxqHA8kbCWsl2tEIr9mCE22RZXSoko9X51qcOHghltRlgjd2x-hw20-BrnGMllpbcQw9kcADaI3x0_DonsFoUqvpNvMl9VP00I8zY64uovKgSQXvYONeapK8-lpB6I8iDvXF4OCf59GmnU8J-VmVM5j4aFjd0_ObRR8klAVa1r6WaeHPr5OpdnphgYpSY" style="">
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-background via-background/60 to-transparent"></div>
<div class="absolute bottom-12 left-12 max-w-xl">
<h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-on-surface mb-4 italic" style="">"The technology we build for you is the last moat you'll ever need to dig."</h3>
<div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
<div class="w-12 h-[1px] bg-accent"></div>
<span class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-accent" style="">Lead Architect, GLODINAS</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Final CTA Section -->
<section class="bg-surface-container rounded-xl p-12 text-center relative overflow-hidden border border-accent/20">
<div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-accent to-transparent opacity-50"></div>
<h2 class="text-[2.25rem] font-black tracking-tighter mb-6" style="">Ready to Scale Your Industry Reach?</h2>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 font-medium text-lg" style="">
                Whether you're in specialized real estate or high-compliance business services, our roadmap starts with your objectives.
            </p>
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-6">
<a href="/book-a-call" class="w-full md:w-auto px-10 py-4 bg-accent text-primary font-bold rounded-lg accent-glow hover:scale-105 transition-all">Get Started</a>
<a href="/our-work" class="w-full md:w-auto px-10 py-4 bg-transparent border border-outline-variant text-on-surface font-bold rounded-lg hover:bg-surface-container-highest transition-all">View Portfolio</a>
</div>
</section>
</main>

</BaseLayout>
